oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Fantabulous Rock and Roll Show 1957
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Five color half sheet (yellow, blue, black, light blue, and red on white) announcing the Rock and Roll Show '57 with Ruth Brown, the Coasters, Bo Diddley, the Schoolboys, the Drifters, Smiley Lewis and others at the War Memorial Auditorium on June 24. Poster features metal photoplates.
